OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,FAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,7,Fhas been named the new Children's
OL,8,FLaureate for 2026-2028.
OL,10,FThe best-selling author, known for
OL,11,Fpenning Orangeboy, will take on the
OL,12,Fprestigious role as the foremost
OL,13,Frepresentative of children's
OL,14,Fliterature.
OL,16,FThe Children's Laureate is responsible
OL,17,Ffor promoting reading and children's
OL,18,Fliterature as well as celebrate
OL,19,Fcreativity and storytelling.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
