PN,37502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,FLawrence was presented with the
OL,7,Fbespoke silver Laureate medal by the
OL,8,Foutgoing Children's Laureate, Frank
OL,9,FCottrell-Boyce, at a ceremony on
OL,10,FTuesday at the Barbican Centre in
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,FLawrence said: "My aim is to create a
OL,14,Fnational conversation that champions
OL,15,Fthe benefits of shared reading and
OL,16,Fsociable reading experiences.
OL,18,F"Alongside BookTrust, I'll explore how
OL,19,Fbooks and reading together help
OL,20,Fcommunities connect and cohere,
OL,21,Fespecially in times of fragmentation.
OL,26,@uD@POUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
