FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,F"I'll work with children and adults
OL,7,Fwith diverse experiences and from
OL,8,Fdiverse backgrounds, children and
OL,9,Fadults who may feel undervalued in our
OL,10,Fsociety, to tell their stories. And, I
OL,11,Fwant to celebrate the unsung heroes
OL,12,Fwho bring joy and nurture reading
OL,13,Fcommunities through their work."
OL,15,FManaged by the UK's largest children's
OL,16,Freading charity, BookTrust, and
OL,17,Fsponsored by Waterstones, the title is
OL,18,Fawarded biannually to a renowned
OL,19,Fwriter or illustrator in recognition
OL,20,Fof exceptional talent.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
