OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,FThe award-winning writer has penned
OL,7,Fnovels for children of all ages and
OL,8,Fgenres with her work often centring on
OL,9,Fthe experiences of young people today,
OL,10,Fexploring themes of inclusivity and
OL,11,Frepresenting diverse family structures.
OL,13,FLawrence published her debut young
OL,14,Fadult novel, Orangeboy, in 2016, which
OL,15,Ffollows 16-year-old Marlon as he finds
OL,16,Fhis world unravel after a date ends in
OL,17,Fa horrible tragedy leading him to be
OL,18,Fhunted by gangs as he tries to protect
OL,19,Fthe ones he loves.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
