PN,37505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,FThe thriller went on to win The
OL,7,FBookseller's YA Book Prize, the
OL,8,FWaterstones Children's Book Prize for
OL,9,FOlder Children's Fiction and was
OL,10,Fshortlisted for the Costa Children's
OL,11,FBook Award.
OL,13,FShe has since published 16 books,
OL,14,Fincluding Needle, People Like Stars,
OL,15,FIs That Your Mama?, Granny Came Here
OL,16,Fon the Empire Windrush, Our Story
OL,17,FStarts in Africa and The Elemental
OL,18,FDetectives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
