PN,37506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,FDiana Gerald, co-chief executive at
OL,7,FBookTrust, said: "All our work and
OL,8,Fresearch at BookTrust shows that books
OL,9,Fcan open conversations and deepen
OL,10,Funderstanding for children, and that
OL,11,Fshared reading experiences create a
OL,12,Fsense of belonging and safety.
OL,14,F"When children, families and
OL,15,Fcommunities don't see themselves
OL,16,Freflected in books, they can struggle
OL,17,Fto find their place in the world.
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
