PN,37507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,F"In this National Year of Reading, the
OL,7,Fappointment of Patrice Lawrence as
OL,8,FChildren's Laureate gives a much-
OL,9,Fneeded voice to the vulnerable
OL,10,Fchildren pushed to the edge of our
OL,11,Fsociety.
OL,13,F"We're looking forward to supporting
OL,14,Fher work with communities across the
OL,15,Fcountry to explore how sharing stories
OL,16,Fcan strengthen wellbeing, build
OL,17,Frelationships and nurture meaningful
OL,18,Fcommunity connection."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
