PN,37508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,FLawrence was made an MBE for services
OL,7,Fto literature in 2021 and later
OL,8,Felected a Fellow of the Royal Society
OL,9,Fof Literature in 2023.
OL,11,FKate Edwards, chair of the Waterstones
OL,12,FChildren's Laureate 2026-28 judging
OL,13,Fpanel, added: "Patrice's remarkable
OL,14,Fwriting for children of all ages draws
OL,15,Fupon topics that are relevant to many
OL,16,Fyoung people's everyday lives,
OL,17,Fcreating a safe space for them to
OL,18,Fexplore complex, sometimes difficult,
OL,19,Fissues.
OL,26,@uD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
