FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1783691326
OL,3,CAward-winning author Patrice Lawrence
OL,4,Cnamed as new Children's Laureate
OL,6,F"In the challenging world we find
OL,7,Fourselves, the connections that books
OL,8,Fand reading offer are more important
OL,9,Fthan ever."
OL,11,FLawrence follows in the footsteps of
OL,12,Fprevious Children's Laureate's
OL,13,Fincluding Sir Quentin Blake (1999-
OL,14,F2001), Dame Jacqueline Wilson (2005-
OL,15,F2007), Dame Julia Donaldson (2011-
OL,16,F2013) and Joseph Coelho (2022-2024).
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
